# 📊 GLevel — Learning Analytics System

## 📌 Overview
GLevel is a data-driven analytics platform that complements GeniUs by tracking and analyzing user study behavior.

It transforms raw study data into meaningful insights through interactive dashboards.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Monitor study time
- Identify learning gaps
- Provide personalized insights
- Support data-driven study strategies

---

## 🖥️ Web Version

### Features
- Interactive dashboards
- Performance graphs
- Subject comparison
- Progress tracking

### Technologies
- Python (data processing)
- Power BI / Streamlit
- SQLite / Firebase

---

## 📱 Mobile Version

### Features
- Simplified dashboards
- Quick performance insights
- Mobile-friendly charts

### Differences from Web
- Reduced data density
- Focus on key metrics
- Faster navigation

---

## 📊 Data Flow
GeniUs Data → API → GLevel Processing → Visualization Dashboard

---

## 🧠 Analytics Engine

- Time tracking per subject
- Difficulty mapping
- Performance trends
- Predictive insights (future)

---

## 🚀 Future Improvements

- AI-based recommendations
- Real-time sync with GeniUs
- Advanced predictive analytics
- Custom study plans

---

## 🏆 Key Highlights

- Data-driven learning approach
- Integration with GeniUs
- Interactive visualization
- Scalable analytics system